CASE WHEN COALESCE(APPLIC_DATE,'') <> '' AND APPLIC_DATE <> '20691231' 
THEN to_date(TRIM(APPLIC_DATE), 'yyyy-MM-dd') WHEN APPLIC_DATE = '20691231' THEN to_date('9999-12-31',
'yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-dd') END
